like we\'ve paid the price for the human race caring so much about each other, preventing casualties of the good humans and keeping the evil ones living to face up for what they\'ve done by making a huge mess of greenhouse gases like carbon dioxide. Some people like me want to curb the human population by 7 billion to 5 billion. Some would rather live with the countless lives that flood our planet, at the expense of other species.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:4:{s:3:\"rel\";s:7:\"replies\";s:4:\"type\";s:20:\"application/atom+xml\";s:4:\"href\";s:72:\"http://miletich2.blogspot.com/feeds/8115494074838958093/comments/default\";s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"Post Comments\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:4:{s:3:\"rel\";s:7:\"replies\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"text/html\";s:4:\"href\";s:86:\"http://www.blogger.com/comment.g?blogID=3424051896540341526&postID=8115494074838958093\";s:5:\"title\";s:10:\"0 Comments\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"edit\";s:4:\"type\";s:20:\"application/atom+xml\";s:4:\"href\";s:82:\"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/3424051896540341526/posts/default/8115494074838958093\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:20:\"application/atom+xml\";s:4:\"href\";s:82:\"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/3424051896540341526/posts/default/8115494074838958093\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"a