vy addiction to the Batman Arkham series of video games. I don\'t know how I\'m gonna get over the Batman Arkhamverse since it\'s my very favorite of the Batman franchise. What should I do? Play a different game like Skyrim?<br /><br />This Saturday is the first Saturday I work at Nifty Thrift. Though it\'s fortunate I get a day off on Monday, I am unsure if it will be the Monday before or after the Saturday I work at the store. I could have my mom or dad take me to the store by 10:00. Otherwise, I\'d go with plan B, a.k.a. taking the bus. But I\'m not sure about taking the bus back home, since the bus service is limited on weekends. <br /><br /><br />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:4:{s:3:\"rel\";s:7:\"replies\";s:4:\"type\";s:20:\"application/atom+xml\";s:4:\"href\";s:72:\"http://miletich2.blogspot.com/feeds/2939546388839700783/comments/default\";s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"Post Comments\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:4:{s:3:\"rel\";s:7:\"replies\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"text/html\";s:4:\"href\";s:86:\"http://www.blogger.com/comment.g?blogID=3424051896540341526&postID=2939546388839700783\";s:5:\"title\";s:10:\"0 Comments\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"edit\";s:4:\"type\";s:20:\"application/atom+xml\";s:4:\"href\";s:82:\"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/3424051896540341526/posts/default/2939546388839700783\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:20:\"application/atom+xml\";s:4