ve officially announced their divorce. I once thought all divorces ended in partners having contempt and hatred for ech other. But that\'s only after one partner feels animosity towards the other for infidelity, spousal abuse or other crimes. But now I see divorce as a reset switch, to undo any destructive changes that\'s happened in their lives.<div><br></div><div>Usually, I thought partners who love each other stay together until the very end. But some split couples could choose to remain friends. Hopefully Ty and Jewel will still hold that.</div>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:4:{s:3:\"rel\";s:7:\"replies\";s:4:\"type\";s:20:\"application/atom+xml\";s:4:\"href\";s:72:\"http://miletich2.blogspot.com/feeds/3494187352376401253/comments/default\";s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"Post Comments\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:4:{s:3:\"rel\";s:7:\"replies\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"text/html\";s:4:\"href\";s:86:\"http://www.blogger.com/comment.g?blogID=3424051896540341526&postID=3494187352376401253\";s:5:\"title\";s:10:\"0 Comments\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"edit\";s:4:\"type\";s:20:\"application/atom+xml\";s:4:\"href\";s:82:\"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/3424051896540341526/posts/default/3494187352376401253\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:20:\"application/atom+xml\";s:4:\"href\";s:82:\"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/3424051896540341526/posts/default/3494187352376401253\";}}s