://meyerweb.com/eric/thoughts/2014/06/09/in-memoriam-2/\">Gedenken an Rebecca</a>.</p>\n<blockquote><p>It’s so easy to do, there’s no reason not to. Go to Twitter on 12 June and post the hashtag #663399Becca along with any additional words or pictures you feel moved to share. Or just share the hashtag. It will not be enough. Nothing will ever be enough. But it will be something.<br />\n<cite><a href=\"http://www.zeldman.com/2014/06/10/the-color-purple/\">Zeldman trifft es in seinem Artikel The Color Purple</a></cite></p></blockquote>\n<hr>\n<p><img src=\"http://bueltge.de/favicon.ico\" alt=\"bueltge.de Favicon\"/> <small>&copy; <a href=\"http://bueltge.de/\">Frank B&uuml;ltge</a>, All rights reserved / Alle Rechte vorbehalten. (ID: 6e8b33de4342c4f2ca76b245199aeee8)</small></p>\n<p>Danke für das Abonnieren meines <strong><a href=\"http://bueltge.de/feed/\">Feed</a></strong>! Inhalt gefällt? <a href=\"http://bueltge.de/wunschliste/\" title=\"Wunschliste\">Danke sagen</a> &middot; <a href=\"http://bueltge.de/663399/4315/#respond\" title=\"zu den Kommentaren dieses Artikels\">Kommentieren</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"Immer im Kreis und doch vorwärts\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"http://bueltge.de/immer-im-kreis-und-doch-vorwaerts/4306/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"http://bueltge.de/immer-im-kreis-und-doch-vorwaerts/4306/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0