PermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:418:\"Product: All WonderPlugin Products Question: In the plugin, settings menu, I checked the option \"Add plugin js scripts to the footer\", but the plugin js files are not added to the WordPress footer. Answer: The plugin is using WordPress hook &#8230; <a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-carousel-plugin/add-plugin-js-files-to-footer-is-not-working/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"WonderPlugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1058:\"<p><strong>Product</strong>:</p>\n<p>All WonderPlugin Products</p>\n<p><strong>Question</strong>:</p>\n<p>In the plugin, settings menu, I checked the option \"Add plugin js scripts to the footer\", but the plugin js files are not added to the WordPress footer.</p>\n<p><strong>Answer</strong>:</p>\n<p>The plugin is using WordPress hook wp_footer to print the plugin js scripts to the footer. wp_footer is one of the most essential theme hooks.</p>\n<p>The problem is because your WordPress theme does not call the WordPress function wp_footer() and the hook is not enabled. Please contact your WordPress theme provider and ask for how to support the wp_footer hook.</p>\n<p>For more details about wp_footer hook and wp_footer() function, please view: <a href=\"https://codex.wordpress.org/Plugin_API/Action_Reference/wp_footer\" target=\"_blank\">https://codex.wordpress.org/Plugin_API/Action_Reference/wp_footer</a> and <a href=\"https://codex.wordpress.org/Function_Reference/wp_footer\" target=\"_blank\">https://codex.wordpress.org/Function_Reference/wp_footer</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"How to create WordPress Portfolio with Categories\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:99:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-tutorials/how-to-create-wordpress-portfolio-with-categories/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sun, 06 Mar 2016 09:24:16 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"WordPress Grid Gallery\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"WordPress Portfolio Plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/?p=3338\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:454:\"Product WonderPlugin Portfolio Grid Gallery This tutorial will guide you how to create WordPress portfolio with categories with WordPress plugin WonderPlugin Portfolio Grid Gallery. You can view the online demo at WordPress Portfolio with Categories. Step 1 - Define categories &#8230; <a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-tutorials/how-to-create-wordpress-portfolio-with-categories/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"WonderPlugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5499:\"<h2>Product<br />\n<h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-gridgallery/\" target=\"_blank\">WonderPlugin Portfolio Grid Gallery</a></p>\n<p>This tutorial will guide you how to create WordPress portfolio with categories with WordPress plugin <a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-gridgallery/\" target=\"_blank\">WonderPlugin Portfolio Grid Gallery</a>.</p>\n<p>You can view the online demo at <a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-gridgallery/\" target=\"_blank\">WordPress Portfolio with Categories</a>.</p>\n<p><span id=\"more-3338\"></span></p>\n<h2>Step 1 - Define categories</h2>\n<p>In WonderPlugin Portfolio Grid Gallery plugin, create a new gallery or edit an existing gallery, in the General Options section, click the link Add Category.</p>\n<p><a class=\"wplightbox\" href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-gallery.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-3348\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-gallery-600x172.png\" alt=\"WordPress Portfolio with Categories\" width=\"600\" height=\"172\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3348\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-gallery-600x172.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-gallery-240x69.png 240w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-gallery-768x220.png 768w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-gallery-500x143.png 500w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-gallery.png 782w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>In the Add Category dialog, enter text for the category caption and slug. By using URL parameter wpcategory, the slug can be used to hyperlink to the specified category on page load. For example, the following link will open the Video category on page load: <a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-gridgallery/?wpcategory=video\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-gridgallery/?wpcategory=video</a>.</p>\n<p><a class=\"wplightbox\" href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-images-videos-category.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-3349\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-images-videos-category-600x160.png\" alt=\"WordPress Portfolio with Categories\" width=\"600\" height=\"160\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3349\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-images-videos-category-600x160.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-images-videos-category-240x64.png 240w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-images-videos-category-768x205.png 768w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-images-videos-category-500x133.png 500w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-images-videos-category.png 911w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>Step 2 - Add images and videos</h2>\n<p>In the plugin, step 1, click Add Image or Add Video button, all defined categories will be listed on the popup dialog. You can select one or multiple categories for the image and video.</p>\n<p><a class=\"wplightbox\" href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-tags.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-3350\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-tags-600x572.png\" alt=\"WordPress Portfolio with Categories\" width=\"600\" height=\"572\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3350\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-tags-600x572.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-tags-189x180.png 189w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-tags-768x732.png 768w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-tags-315x300.png 315w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-tags.png 865w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>Step 3 - Show category buttons</h2>\n<p>In the plugin, step 4, Options tab, Category Options, check the option \"Show categories buttons\". You can also select position and CSS style for the buttons.</p>\n<p><a class=\"wplightbox\" href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-category-buttons.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-3351\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-category-buttons-600x306.png\" alt=\"WordPress Portfolio with Categories\" width=\"600\" height=\"306\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3351\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-category-buttons-600x306.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-category-buttons-240x122.png 240w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-category-buttons-768x392.png 768w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-category-buttons-500x255.png 500w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/wordpress-portfolio-category-buttons.png 982w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:89:\"How to load image and video list from a json web service in WonderPlugin Portfolio plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:139:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-tutorials/how-to-load-image-and-video-list-from-a-json-web-service-in-wonderplugin-portfolio-plugin/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sun, 28 Feb 2016 00:59:51 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"WordPress Grid Gallery\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"WordPress Grid Gallery Lightbox\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26: